TITLE: Payment Method Implementation in OpenCart 4.0.2.0 (New Format)
DESCRIPTION: Updated implementation of payment methods in OpenCart 4.0.2.0. This new format includes an option_data array and changes 'title' to 'name' to support multiple payment options per payment extension.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: PHP
CODE:
```
$method_data = [];

if ($status) {
    $option_data['bank_transfer'] = [
        'code' => 'bank_transfer.bank_transfer',
        'name' => $this->language->get('heading_title')
    ];

    $method_data = [
        'code'       => 'bank_transfer',
        'name'       => $this->language->get('heading_title'),
        'option'     => $option_data,
        'sort_order' => $this->config->get('payment_bank_transfer_sort_order')
    ];
}
```

