TITLE: Running the Promise Task Queue in an Event Loop
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to run the promise task queue to ensure promises are resolved in an asynchronous event loop context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/guzzlehttp/promises/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
// Get the global task queue
$queue = GuzzleHttp\Promise\Utils::queue();
$queue->run();
```

