TITLE: Rejection Forwarding with Exception Handling
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how exceptions thrown in rejection callbacks are forwarded to subsequent rejection callbacks in the promise chain.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/guzzlehttp/promises/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
use GuzzleHttp\Promise\Promise;

$promise = new Promise();
$promise->then(null, function ($reason) {
    throw new Exception($reason);
})->then(null, function ($reason) {
    assert($reason->getMessage() === 'Error!');
});

$promise->reject('Error!');
```

