TITLE: Configuring Multiple Axes in Flot (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure multiple x and y axes in Flot charts. It shows how to set up a single x axis at the top and two y axes, with the second y axis positioned on the right and having a minimum value of 20.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/admin/view/javascript/jquery/flot/API.md#2025-04-19_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
{
    xaxes: [ { position: "top" } ],
    yaxes: [ { }, { position: "right", min: 20 } ]
}
```

