TITLE: Setting POST Fields and Files in Guzzle 4.x
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to set POST fields and add files to a request body using the new PostBody interface in Guzzle 4.x. This replaces the previous methods on the request object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/guzzlehttp/guzzle/UPGRADING.md#2025-04-19_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: PHP
CODE:
```
$request = $client->createRequest('POST', '/');
$request->getBody()->setField('foo', 'bar');
$request->getBody()->addFile(new PostFile('file_key', fopen('/path/to/content', 'r')));
```

