TITLE: Enabling Deprecation Warnings in Guzzle
DESCRIPTION: Code snippet showing how to enable E_USER_DEPRECATED warnings in Guzzle to identify usage of deprecated methods. This allows developers to identify code that needs updating.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/guzzlehttp/guzzle/UPGRADING.md#2025-04-19_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
\Guzzle\Common\Version::$emitWarnings = true;
```

