TITLE: Native Function Calls in Guzzle 7.0
DESCRIPTION: Example showing the change in internal native function calls in Guzzle 7.0, where all functions are now prefixed with a slash for better method overloading protection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/guzzlehttp/guzzle/UPGRADING.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
// Before:
curl_version();

// After:
\curl_version();
```

