TITLE: Demonstrating Promise as Deferred Pattern in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Shows how a promise in GuzzleHttp is also the deferred value, allowing direct resolution of the promise.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/guzzlehttp/promises/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$promise = new Promise();
$promise->then(function ($value) { echo $value; });
// The promise is the deferred value, so you can deliver a value to it.
$promise->resolve('foo');
// prints "foo"
```

