TITLE: Namespacing Flot Plugins with IIFE in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to wrap a plugin in an Immediately Invoked Function Expression (IIFE) to avoid name collisions with other libraries and ensure jQuery compatibility.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/admin/view/javascript/jquery/flot/PLUGINS.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
(function ($) {
    // plugin definition
    // ...
})(jQuery);
```

