TITLE: Appending Content to PSR-7 HTTP Message Body in PHP
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to append content to a PSR-7 message body using the write() method of StreamInterface.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/psr/http-message/docs/PSR7-Usage.md#2025-04-19_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
$response->getBody()->write('Hello'); // writing directly
$body = $request->getBody(); // which is a `StreamInterface`
$body->write('xxxxx');
```

