TITLE: Custom Point Symbol Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement a custom cross symbol for data points using canvas drawing operations. Includes context parameters and sizing calculations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/admin/view/javascript/jquery/flot/API.md#2025-04-19_snippet_34

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function cross(ctx, x, y, radius, shadow) {
    var size = radius * Math.sqrt(Math.PI) / 2;
    ctx.moveTo(x - size, y - size);
    ctx.lineTo(x + size, y + size);
    ctx.moveTo(x - size, y + size);
    ctx.lineTo(x + size, y - size);
}
```

