TITLE: Creating Streaming Responses in Guzzle 4.x
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to create a streaming response using the new 'stream' option in Guzzle 4.x. This replaces the previous PhpStreamRequestFactory approach used in Guzzle 3.x.
SOURCE: https://github.com/opencart/opencart/blob/master/upload/system/storage/vendor/guzzlehttp/guzzle/UPGRADING.md#2025-04-19_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: PHP
CODE:
```
// 3.0
use Guzzle\Stream\PhpStreamRequestFactory;
$request = $client->get('/');
$factory = new PhpStreamRequestFactory();
$stream = $factory->fromRequest($request);
$data = $stream->read(1024);

